This small shrine is dedicated to the Keeper, the purported mysterious entity inhabiting Iceflow Island. The locals leave these across the wilds in various locations, usually bringing offerings there in the hopes of appeasing him, gaining his favor or simply in an expression of respect. Its unclear if the Keeper ever comes to actually collect, or if its simply the wildlife and Iceflow Islands rough climate which take care of the offerings.
